    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "The blade of this *+2 greater striking holy standard-grade cold iron elven curve blade* shines with a pale fire that illuminates the wielder\u2019s face in a grim visage and produces dim light in a 10-foot emanation. The wielder can suppress or reactivate this light as a single action with the concentrate trait.",
