                    "frequency": "once per hour",
                    "effect": "You brandish  *Morning Glow* and focus on its gleaming light, boosting its illumination so that it produces bright light in a 30-foot emanation (and dim light for another 30 feet) for 10 minutes. All creatures in this area that have the demon trait must attempt a DC 31 Reflex save.",
